function_call.arguments: {"risks":[{"Description":"Bias in data collection due to online survey","Impact":"Misrepresentation of population demographics and characteristics leading to inaccurate conclusions","Mitigation":"Supplement online survey with offline methods to capture the perspectives of those without online access","Technologies":"Offline survey tools, community outreach programs","People":"Population not well represented in online surveys","Owner":"Research team, government agencies"},{"Description":"Incomplete questionnaire submissions","Impact":"Data accuracy and integrity compromised","Mitigation":"Implement stricter validation checks and error notifications during questionnaire completion","Technologies":"Online survey validation tools, error detection algorithms","People":"Survey respondents","Owner":"Research team, survey platform administrators"},{"Description":"Logic errors in returned questionnaires","Impact":"Invalid data affecting the reliability of analyses","Mitigation":"Implement pre-screening logic checks and conduct thorough data cleaning processes","Technologies":"Automated logic check algorithms, data cleaning software","People":"Research team, data analysts","Owner":"Research team, data analysts"}]}
